Jeremy is an advisor to Escape to El Salvador, a community of professionals brought together to help you apply for legal residency and citizenship in El Salvador. Prior to that, he volunteered at a Bitcoin Help Desk, where he offered free support installing and running nodes, and hosted several 'hackdays' including for the Blockstream Satellite. He is also an open source contributor to several Bitcoin projects.